description: Data was generated from file metadata information from a sync to GDC legacy archive on January 2019.

fields.description: Id of the Project -- e.g. eg TCGA-BRCA, TARGET-AML, etc
fields.name: project_id

fields.description: Name of file at the GDC
fields.name: file_name

fields.description: 128-bit hash value expressed as a 32 digit hexadecimal number (in lower case) used as a file's digital fingerprint
fields.name: md5

fields.description: File state -- either submitted or released
fields.name: state

fields.description: UUID that all versions of the data (in other words, all GUIDs) point to
fields.name: baseid

fields.description: Access Control List -- if access is controlled, this field contains the dbGaP accession, eg phs000179
fields.name: acl

fields.description: Description of the data, eg. clinical_supplement, aligned_reads
fields.name: type

fields.description: Reason for removal from the GDC
fields.name: deletereason
